  <slide>
    <title>Summary</title>
    <contents>
      <ul>
        <li>Accessibility must be intergated into main stream development and authoring.</li>
        <li>More people must understand accessibility.</li>
        <li>Need technologies that support accessible design.</li>
        <li>Authoring environments support accessibility by default, instead of by exception.</li>
        <li>Many opportunities to learn and share information in communities of practice.</li>
      </ul>
    </contents>
